This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=2617

* Regular expression highlighting (from perl)
* Should work in all versions of vim, properly disabling the features for v7+
* COMPLETE recognition of all settings with a good understanding of syntax
* Settings recognized include all plugins shipped with SA plus a few 3rd-party plugins.

Spell-check is enabled on various pieces for which it is appropriate (vim 7+, you must turn it on first).

This has also been posted to the spamassassin users mailing list.
